# Planning artifact parity (Skillgrid paths)

Canonical locations for durable planning intent so agents do not invent parallel sources of truth. This hub uses OpenSpec plus PRD plus handoff files instead of a single flat doc tree.

| Planning notion | Skillgrid location |
| --- | --- |
| **Vision / initiative** | **`.skillgrid/prd/`** — `INDEX.md`, `PRD*` files |
| **Scope / requirements** | **`openspec/changes/<change-id>/proposal.md`**, **`specs/**/spec.md`**, **`tasks.md`** |
| **Milestones / phases** | PRD index and execution snapshots — **`docs/02-workflow-usage.md`**, **`docs/03-skillgrid-logic.md`** |
| **Current step & decisions** | **`.skillgrid/tasks/context_<change-id>.md`**, **`events/<change-id>.jsonl`**, optional Engram state topic per **`engram-convention.md`** |
| **Implementation-phase context** | **`openspec/changes/<change-id>/design.md`**, slice specs, handoff **Decisions** sections |

Agents must **not** bury scope-only updates in chat — update these paths or Engram topics.
